Package: calibratedMRP
Title: Calibrated Multilevel Regression and Poststratification
Version: 0.0.1.0000
Authors@R: 
    person("William", "Marble", , "marble.will@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9352-5540"))
Description: Provides tools for small area estimation using multilevel 
    regression and poststratification (MRP). Provides a user-friendly interfaces enabling researchers to calibrate MRP predictions to known population targets at arbitrary levels of geography. Estimates of outcomes without known population targets can be unpdated using the calibration procedure developed in Marble and Clinton (2025).
